column2: Initiating, pioneering energy. Independent, bold, courageous, assertive, fiery, inspirational, direct, and decisive. Can be egotistical, impulsive, impatient, aggressive, and lacking in subtlety.
Stable, enduring, unyielding, and acquisitive, with strong values and desires. Can be stuck, stubborn, overly possessive, and self-indulgent.
Agile, versatile, inquisitive, flowing, and conversational. Can be volatile, superficial, changeable, restless, and inconsistent.
Nurturing, protective, tenacious, and emotionally sensitive, with strong roots. Can be overly protective, unwilling to let go, timid, and reclusive.
Self-confident, generous, warm-hearted, authoritative, and dramatic. Can be overly proud, vain, extravagant, and arrogant.
Meticulous, discriminating, pure, practical, health-conscious, and hard-working. Can be hyper-critical, petty, and perfectionistic.
Even-handed, harmonious, artistic, diplomatic, and balanced, with a strong sense of fairness. Can be over-compromising, appeasing, and judgmental.
Intense, magnetic, and perceptive, with a power to confront. Can be destructive, vengeful, jealous, and overly dramatic.
Inspiring, visionary, enthusiastic, goal-seeking, truthful, and adventurous. Can be reckless, unrestrained, and tactless.
Disciplined, responsible, reliable, industrious, conscientious, practical, and achievement-oriented. Can be pessimistic, overly conventional, rigid, materialistic, and callous.
Humanitarian, innovative, group-conscious, progressive, and altruistic. Can be rebellious, eccentric, aloof, emotionally superficial, and overly extroverted.
Compassionate, sensitive, self-sacrificing, gentle, and intuitive. Can be escapist, impractical, hyper-sensitive, and gullible.
